channel.title: Favorite Skateboarding Videos?
channel.description:
What are your favorite skateboarding videos?
Video that inspired me to start skating - [url=http://youtube.com/watch?v=TZ4XPpXK3kI]Daewon Song in Almost Round Three[/url]
Favorite video from the '80s - [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y-PQjKVuGUM]Tommy Guerrero in Future Primitive[/url]
Favorite skate style - [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jvWqAm-iU_o]Matt Hensley in Shackle Me Not [/url]
Second favorite style [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zH9Ty0a1Eo8]Mark Gonzales doing his thing[/url]
Most insane skating - [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=js40oQFAq80]Danny Way in DC Video[/url]
Most fun video to watch - [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y4DhYlaYpE0]NYC section - Future Primitive[/url]
